David White (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_White_(actor) 0 David White (April 4, 1916 – November 27, 1990) was an American stage, film and television actor best known for playing Darrin Stephens' boss Larry Tate on the 1964–72 ABC situation comedy Bewitched.
